Mrs. Merchant underwent laparoscopic-assisted  low-anterior resection for a colon cancer on May 3, 2010. She calls today with an update on her progress. She states she is doing well. Her appetite has returned to normal. She is having one-to-two soft stools a day. She will keep us informed of her progress.

